reviews.text: less air conditions in this hot weather, the food is quite good
Chinese seafood restaurant,  nice for group gatherings and functions. Food is above average for the price. Restaurant Chain with many locations.

Terrible customer service. Will give a negative rating if possible. Served a dish that we did not order and showed us a "proof" that we were certained it was altered. Please take a picture of the order slip before submitting. Maybe even counter sign beside every tick you made would be a wise move. End up we got to paid for a dish we didn't order and spoiled our experience. The manager argued her way out in a rude manner and forced us to accept the dish.
Decent food at reasonable price. Will recommend the Peking duck which can be sold out quickly. 北京填鴨值得推介 但要儘早order
A typical chinese restaurant. Been there having a yum cha during lunch time with friends, service and food are OK. Price reasonable.

出品欠佳，冷氣唔夠，服務一般，商場內出入方便，環境尚可。

這區住的老人家很多及大多數是內地移民 酒樓的清潔一般 招呼亦只屬一般
